Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.97,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.27,0:00:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah siuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kabura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kondisimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kurasa lumayan baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Benarkah? Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}buka bajumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Buka saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Dasar tukang buka baju orang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau tampaknya baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.74,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, ada apa di perutku ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tanya saja pada mereka yang terlibat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku di sini hanya sebagai perawat RS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Mereka yang terlibat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8\i1}Aku baru ingat,\Nperutku tadi tertembak pistol, 'kan?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi tak terasa sakit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa mungkin itu khayalanku saja?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku mengantuk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Pagi, Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa? Nona Detek...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.66,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf sedalam-dalamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah kau masih hidup.\NKau merasa sakit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku benar-benar tertembak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku tak sengaja menembakmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dia mencoba menghentikan\Nupaya bunuh diriku, lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Itu kecelakaan!\NAku tak bermaksud menembaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku, Nanakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Akan kubawa dia ke RS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}RS-nya Kabura pasti bisa merawatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Lalu, aku akan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kenapa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.97,0:04:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah Nona Detektif masih hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Banyak hal terjadi, tapi semuanya\Nmasih hidup dengan riang gembira?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa aku
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}sudah menjadi vam...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Mau kuperiksa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bercanda saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau masih manusia\Nkarena kuperiksa denyut nadimu masih ada,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}beda halnya dengan vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}- Tapi...\N- Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Berkat pertolonganmu,\Naku batal bunuh diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Selama ini, kujalani hidupku dengan\Nmemikirkan cara membunuh vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dendam pada vampir yang menghancurkan\Nkeluargaku membuatku menyimpan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu itu tetap ada dalam hatiku\Nkarena aku melampiaskan amarahku
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}terhadap vampir yang mengubah ayahku\Npada semua vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi hari ini, sesuatu itu\Nbenar-benar sudah hilang dari hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu alasanmu mau bunuh diri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi mati itu menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Keinginan untuk bunuh diri itu\Nselalu muncul samar-samar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Setiap kali keinginan itu datang,\Nkuingat amarahku agar aku tetap hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu amarah ini tak nyata,\Nmelainkan dusta belaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kulampiaskan amarahku sepuluh tahun ini\Npada vampir karena ayahku direnggut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku sudah lelah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Diriku sekarang hanyalah wanita tua
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}yang hampa, membosankan,\Ndan hidupnya stagnan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Yamori, aku sudah keliru\Nmemilih jalan hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mampu meraih satu pun keinginanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kumohon, tolong jangan menjadi sepertiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kumohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kupikir-pikir,\Ndia sudah seperti ini dari awal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia selalu mencemaskanku.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nona Detektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kurasa wanita berusia 40 tahun masih muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sepuluh tahun yang lalu,\Nkau kelas tiga SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, usiamu sekarang 27\Natau 28 tahun, 'kan, Nona Detektif?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baru menginjak 28 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hari ulang tahunmu bertepatan\Ndengan Halloween. Selamat ulang tahun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Setelah sepuluh tahun berlalu,\Nbaru ini ada yang mengucapkannya padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei. Yamori sudah siuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kalian sudah bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf padanya,\Ntapi dia malah menghiburku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nanakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau jatuh cinta padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku wanita yang biasa-biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Masa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ramai sekali di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Menghabiskan waktu sepuluh tahun\Nuntuk membasmi vampir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Rencananya agak ceroboh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nona Detektif sendiri yang bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Lantas, kenapa dia harus\Nmengulur-ulur waktu untuk bunuh diri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa tindakanku mencegahnya bunuh diri itu\Nmemang benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.44,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti sudah mati\Njika dia memang mau mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa semudah itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Itu tugasmu untuk memikirkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau harus masuk ke sekolah\Npaling tidak sekali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sebab jika kau tiba-tiba menghilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei. Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tidak! Tidak ada apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Alasanku tak mau Nona Detektif mati\Nkarena Nazuna pasti akan sangat sedih.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Nazuna saja sempat menangis.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu pertama kalinya kulihat dia menangis.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mungkin aku mau Nazuna selalu tersenyum.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Entah bagaimana kabar Nazuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nazuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hai. Aku mau mengembalikan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nona detektif itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Beri aku rokok.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Padahal baru saja kubeli.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei, kau lihat kejadian tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kudengar ada syuting\Nadegan penembakan sebuah film.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Katanya bunyi tembakannya terdengar asli.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, mereka menganggapnya syuting film\Njika tak ada mayat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Rencanaku memang gagal total.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau, aku bisa menghiburmu\Nsemalam suntuk. Bercanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Malam lebih baik dihabiskan\Ndengan sunyi, sepi, sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}aku rasanya mau minum tipis-tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Akan kurahasiakan dari istrimu\Nhanya untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baik! Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan mengajakku berselingkuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nazuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ko, aku seharusnya bertindak sesuatu tadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}tapi maafkan aku karena tak mampu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Rasanya menyedihkan karena malah selalu\Nsisi payahku yang kuperlihatkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ko, terima kasih sudah menyelamatkannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan ini? Kau membuatku takut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ini juga pasti berat bagimu\Nkarena kau selalu mencemaskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan sedih begitu,\Nkarena semuanya baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}- Jadi...\N- Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sudah sembuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau boleh keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.01,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Selamat atas kesembuhanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tembakan konfeti ini kurang cocok, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku baru tertembak pistol kemarin, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.73,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kabura pun setiap kali kutanya\Nhanya menjawab, "Mana aku tahu?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Berarti kita harus...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Nona...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Potong rambut...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah bisa berjalan-jalan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya, begitulah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bagaimana menurutmu?\NHaruskah kita membahasnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Entahlah, mungkin saat ini,\Ntopik itu masih sensitif untuk dibahas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku datang karena kau meneleponku,\Ntapi jika tak ada apa-apa, aku pergi saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tunggu! Banyak hal\Nyang mau kutanyakan padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}- Boleh aku merokok?\N- Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bir gelas besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Teh oolong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jus jeruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Terserah aku mau minum apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku tak minum alkohol karena mudah mabuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Padahal kita bertemu lagi setelah\Nsama-sama dewasa dan sudah berbaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.93,0:13:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, kurasa pasti seru\Njika bernostalgia sambil minum-minum
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}karena kita sudah lama tak bertemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Maaf, tambah lagi birnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kalian tak melihat sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sesuatu yang berbeda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bagaimana ini?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Haruskah kami membahasnya?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Atau ini tentang hal lain?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bukan, ini tentang rambutnya.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8\i1}Tapi kesempatan untuk menegur rambutnya\Nsudah lewat{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8\i1}karena kami tak langsung menyebutnya\Nketika bertemu tadi.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8\i1}Jadi, rasanya agak aneh\Njika mengatakannya sekarang.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8\i1}Jika kami menegurnya sekarang,\Nberarti kami hanya berbasa-basi saja.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}- Jadi...{\i}\N- Rambutmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.18,0:14:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jangan menegur saja.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Rambutmu bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi beri pendapat!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Menurutmu bagus, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku baru pertama kali pergi ke salon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bagus! Obrolan yang sempurna!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Pertama kali?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya, kurasa hidupku\Nsudah seperti manusia normal sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kalian tahu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kuhabiskan hidupku sepuluh tahun terakhir\Nuntuk mencari cara membunuh vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Waktuku yang terbuang\Ntak akan kembali lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kupikir aku sudah tua\Ndan tak muda lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau masih menganggapku\Nwanita muda, 'kan, Yamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aduh! Kenapa memukulku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku jengkel saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, Nanakusa.\NAku tak akan merebut Yamori di belakangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Diam, Kak!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti akan minta izin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bukan begitu maksudku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Lalu? Pasti ada alasan\Nkenapa kau memanggilku ke sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ya. Tentang tubuhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sudah tumbuh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa yang tumbuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti cemas sudah tumbuh atau belum\Natau tentang ukurannya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}atau penasaran apa punyamu\Nsama dengan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tenang saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku yakin semua pasti berpikir begitu.\NJadi, tak ada gunanya mencemaskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maksudku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Taringnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Taring barumu pasti tumbuh\Nbegitu kau menjadi vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa? Kau berpikir hal kotor, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dasar cabul!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.71,0:15:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sialan! Kurang ajar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.54,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bercanda saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada taring yang tumbuh\Npada gigi Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kita bahas emosi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hal pertama, Yamori,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}kau manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Manusia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak hal yang tak kupahami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, apa yang terjadi\Ndengan luka di perutku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kurasa yang paling tahu vampir\Nbukanlah vampir sendiri,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}tapi manusia yang mengejar vampir,\Nyaitu kau, Nona Detektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Pengetahuanmu sangat berharga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ceritakanlah padaku tentang kaum vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, 'kan?\NDenyut nadimu normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}sedangkan vampir tak punya denyut nadi.\NJadi, artinya Yamori masih manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dia benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Luka tembakan dariku sudah sembuh, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bisa tunjukkan padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Lukanya sudah tertutup cukup rapi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kulit anak muda memang bagus, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kenapa kau gemetaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Pertama kalinya disentuh seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Hei! Jangan genit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau bingung kenapa lukamu\Ncepat tertutup rapat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}padahal kau tak menjadi vampir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau sebenarnya menjadi vampir,\Ntapi hanya sebentar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau hampir menjadi vampir\Nuntuk lebih tepatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.16,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mungkin karena saat itu\Nkondisi hatimu berkecamuk,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}kau pun mengalami lonjakan emosi.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Emosi itu sederhana,\Ntapi kompleks dan samar.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Cinta dan asmara itu serupa,\Ntapi tak sama.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Itu artinya otakmu\Nhampir jatuh cinta pada Nanakusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, itu kebingunganku saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau keliru, Yamori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kebanyakan percintaan di dunia ini\Njustru dimulai dari bingung dan main-main.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu pendapat pribadiku saja,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi intinya, kau tak bisa memastikannya.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.29,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika kau telusuri kebingunganmu itu,\Nrasa itu bisa menjadi nyata.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau hampir menjadi vampir\Nwalau hanya untuk sementara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Bisa dibilang, emosi yang kau rasakan\Nsaat itu memang nyata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:19:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}mungkin rasa cinta\Ndi antara kalian berdua masih lemah,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}tapi kutarik itu.\NMemang ada rasa cinta di antara kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, bagaimana...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Apa saja yang sudah kalian berdua lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kita sekarang tahu Yamori juga punya rasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kalian pasti tahu harus berbuat apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan? Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Dia memang selalu seperti ini, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ini pertama kalinya aku minum dengannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Hei! Jangan bermesraan\Ndi depan orang lain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Dasar menyebalkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tapi bermesraanlah.\NKalian memang harus bermesraan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Pasti kau berkata tanpa sadar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baru minum sedikit saja,\Nkau sudah mabuk berat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kata siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mabuk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Suaramu terlalu keras! Diam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Dengar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kubilang, mudah saja\Nmenipu otakmu jika suasananya mendukung!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tapi sepertinya kalian\Nbelum pernah berbuat macam-macam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, satu-satunya\Nyang Yamori butuhkan saat ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}tak lain dan tak bukan\Nadalah kesenangan seksual!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Hei, ayo kita pulang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.81,0:20:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kalian meremehkan faktor seksual itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sepertinya kau salah paham dengan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.95,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau tak akan tahu kecuali mencobanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Atau bagaimana jika berciuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Ayo kalian berciuman saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku paham! Kalian sudah pernah berciuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Berarti sudah pernah, ya? Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Baiklah.\N- Seperti nenek tua menyebalkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Baiklah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tapi kau tak pernah menciumku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.31,0:21:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Kau sekarang terdengar agak manis\Nseperti dirimu dulu, Kak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.78,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}- Aku...\N- Aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tolong tambah bir lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.91,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Tolong tambah dua gelas bir lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(00,40)}Terjemahan subtitle oleh\NIndra Nugraha Putra
